<div class="mypage_top_background">
  <div class="mypage_top">
    <div class="page-header">
      <h1>マイページ<br>
      <small><%= current_user.name %>さん、こんにちは！</small></h1>
    </div>
    <p>マイページでは学習進捗を確認できます。<br>
       自分の学習進捗に合わせてカリキュラムを選んでください。
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="mypage1_background">
  <div class="mypage1">
    <h2>学習進捗</h2>
    <div class="progress">
      <div id ="answer_progress" class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped active" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow=@aria_valuenow aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100">
        <%= @answer_valuenow  %>%
      </div>
    </div>
    <span>あなたの進捗は<%= @answer_valuenow  %>%です。</span>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="mypage2_background">
  <div class="mypage2">
    <h2>正答率</h2>
    <div class="progress">
      <div id="collect_answer_progress" class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped active" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow=@aria_valuenow aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100">
        <%= @collect_answer_valuenow  %>%
      </div>
    </div>
    <span>あなたは全問題のうち、<%= @collect_answer_valuenow  %>%正解してます。</span>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="mypage3_background">
  <div class="mypage3">
    <h2>カリキュラム</h2>
    <p class="curriculum_btn col-xs-offset-1 col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1"><%= link_to "一問一答に挑戦", itimon_ittous_index_path %></p>
    <p class="curriculum_btn col-xs-offset-1 col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1"><%= link_to "分野別で問題を解く", questions_path %></p>
  </div>
</div>

<script>
$(function(){
  $('#answer_progress').width(gon.answer_valuenow + '%');
  $('#collect_answer_progress').width(gon.collect_answer_valuenow + '%');

});
</script>
